## 5. Interaction Patterns

### 5.1 Keyboard Shortcuts

| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| `Ctrl+C` | Copy selected logs to clipboard |
| `End` | Enable auto-scroll to last message |

### 5.2 Context Menu (Log Items)

| Menu Item | Command | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| Copy | `CopyCommand` | Copy full log entry |
| Copy Only Message | `CopyOnlyMessageCommand` | Copy message text only |
| Exclude system | `ExcludeSystemCommand` | Hide logs from this system |
| Clear | `ClearLogsCommand` | Clear all logs |

### 5.3 Context Menu (Systems Tab)

| Menu Item | Command |
|-----------|---------|
| Clear Unused Systems | `ClearSystemsCacheCommand` |

### 5.4 Column Header Context Menu

- Shows list of all columns
- Checkable menu items to show/hide columns
- Bound to `IsVisible` property of each column

### 5.5 Auto-Scroll Behavior

- Toggle button in toolbar
- When enabled: automatically scrolls to newest log entry
- When disabled: maintains current scroll position
- Automatically disables when user manually selects a log entry

