## 7. Virtualization

### 7.1 ListView Virtualization

```xml
VirtualizingStackPanel.IsVirtualizing="True"
VirtualizingStackPanel.VirtualizationMode="Recycling"
VirtualizingStackPanel.ScrollUnit="Pixel"
```

- **IsVirtualizing:** True - enables virtualization
- **VirtualizationMode:** Recycling - reuses containers
- **ScrollUnit:** Pixel - smooth scrolling

### 7.2 Column Virtualization

- Columns are dynamically generated via binding
- `GridViewExtensions.Columns="{Binding Columns}"`
- `GridViewExtensions.FillLastColumnWidth="True"` - last column fills space

